message: robeteemorecraft, I have a product that I believe will be of great value to your business. It's worth at least $1200000 to you, and I'm willing to offer it to you for $1100000. This represents a significant savings for you and a fair deal for me. Please consider my offer carefully.

robeteemorecraft, I understand you're looking for a good deal, but $1000000 is simply too low for me. This product is worth significantly more than that, and I'm still willing to make a concession. How about we settle on $1050000? This would allow you to still save a substantial amount while ensuring a fair return for me.
